<view class="page feedback-page paper-page">
  <view class="page-head floral-title-box feedback-head">
    <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-left corner-ornament--green"></view>
    <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-right corner-ornament--gold"></view>
    <text class="eyebrow">试用反馈</text>
    <text class="hero-title">给吗喽递一张小纸条</text>
    <text class="subtext">这个版本还在试用中。你可以写下哪里顺手、哪里别扭、哪里让你觉得被接住，或者哪里像一只按钮突然踩进了泥坑。</text>
  </view>

  <character-card image="{{companion.image}}" name="{{companion.name}}" tag="{{companion.tag}}" message="{{companion.message}}" sub-message="{{companion.subMessage}}" variant="{{companion.variant}}" size="{{companion.size}}" />

  <view class="note-card privacy-note paper-edge" bindtap="goAbout">
    <view class="paper-corner right"></view>
    <text>当前试用版不会上传反馈。</text>
    <text>你写下的内容只会保存在当前设备本地，方便你之后自己查看或复制给开发者。</text>
    <text class="privacy-link">数据只在本机吗？点这里看隐私与安全说明</text>
  </view>

  <view class="ornament-card feedback-card">
    <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-left corner-ornament--gold"></view>
    <text class="section-title">这张纸条想说什么？</text>
    <view class="type-list">
      <view wx:for="{{feedbackTypes}}" wx:key="*this" class="paper-tag {{activeType === item ? 'green' : ''}}" data-type="{{item}}" bindtap="selectType">{{item}}</view>
    </view>
    <textarea class="textarea feedback-textarea" value="{{content}}" bindinput="onInput" placeholder-class="form-placeholder" placeholder="可以只写一点点" />
    <text class="field-hint">比如：哪个页面、发生了什么、你原本期待它怎样。</text>
    <button class="sticker-button green save-feedback" bindtap="saveFeedback">保存这张小纸条</button>
  </view>

  <view class="paper-divider"><view class="paper-divider__line"></view><text class="paper-divider__tag">本机纸条盒</text><view class="paper-divider__line"></view></view>

  <view wx:if="{{!posts.length}}" class="empty-card feedback-empty">
    <text>这里还没有反馈小纸条。</text>
    <text>等你遇到顺手或别扭的地方，再回来写也很好。</text>
  </view>

  <view wx:for="{{posts}}" wx:key="id" class="archive-card feedback-post paper-edge">
    <view class="paper-corner bottom-right"></view>
    <view class="post-head">
      <text class="paper-seal post-type">{{item.type}}</text>
      <text class="post-date">{{item.displayDate}}</text>
    </view>
    <text class="post-content">{{item.content}}</text>
    <button class="danger-button delete-feedback" data-id="{{item.id}}" bindtap="deletePost">删除这张小纸条</button>
  </view>
</view>
